    <description><![CDATA[相关扩展——Paste Image 默认快捷键是 ctrl+alt+V 可以修改为ctrl+shift+V 设置 进入setting.json 输入配置信息 &#34;pasteImage.path&#34;: &#34;${currentFileDir}/${currentFileNameWithoutExt}.assets&#34;, &#34;pasteImage.basePath&#34;: &#34;${currentFileDir}&#34;, &#34;pasteImage.forceUnixStyleSeparator&#34;: true, &#34;pasteImage.prefix&#34;: &#34;/&#34;, &#34;pasteImage.insertPattern&#34;: &#34;${imageSyntaxPrefix}./${currentFileNameWithoutExt}.assets/${imageFileName}${imageSyntaxSuffix}&#34;, &#34;pasteImage.defaultName&#34;: &#34;i\\mg-YMMDDHHmmss&#34;,]]></description>
